anong ginagawa mo

00:17:12.270 --> 00:17:13.440
Sa utos ni Prinsipe Li,

00:17:13.440 --> 00:17:14.480
upang matiyak ang kaligtasan ng Crown Prince,

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:14.790
[Tirahan ng Heneral]

